data.description: Introducing a stunning 2-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom with a Den/Office Condo at the prestigious National Harbor, offering over 1200 square feet of luxurious living space.  You'll love the  custom  closets in the primary and secondary bedrooms.  The primary bathroom has a walk-in tub and shower.  This freshly painted gem has refinished hardwood floors and new carpet in the bedrooms.  The modern kitchen with sleek granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances is  perfect for culinary enthusiasts.  One of the highlights of this residence is the breathtaking view of the Potomac River that can be enjoyed  from your own private Juliet balconies.  Imagine sipping your morning coffee while soaking in the serene beauty of the water.  In addition to the exquisite interior, you have your own parking and storage space in the underground garage.  Residents of this building have access to a range of amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle.  Dive into relaxation with the in-ground swimming pool, stay fit in the well-equipped exercise room, or host unforgettable gatherings in the community game room.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this condo your new home and experience the best of National Harbor living.  Schedule a viewing today and prepare to be captivated by this exceptional property.
